The paper proposes a deep learning model for crowd understanding, specifically for crowd counting. Therefore, the most likely category is computer vision (cs.CV). The model also uses attention mechanisms and deformable convolutions, which are common techniques in artificial intelligence (cs.AI) and machine learning (cs.LG). The paper also evaluates the model on multiple datasets, which falls under multimedia (cs.MM) and robotics (cs.RO) categories.
